The blurry ball known as Spike came fast at Warhead, but he easily 
moved clear from the charge. What he did not anticipate was the blast 
charge coming at his backthrusters. He was propelled a few meters 
farther, which made him lose his lock.

Warhead: I will kill all of you pretentious and arrogant Tripredacus! 
Milord Megatron shall never be taken by the likes of you!

He fired his machine guns randomly.

Burrock, burned by the flames, lost hold of the Ant. He steadied his 
aim and shot several spikes at his enemy, all acid-coated.

Burrock: Whaddaya say now, Antie? Scums like you are not even worthy 
of the Tripredacus Strikers!
